Texts.Eng: A display which appears to be connected to some sort of radar.
Texts.Rus: Дисплей, который подключается к чему-то вроде радара.

Texts.Eng: Glasss isss flashing green. Good colour.
I wonder what the purpose of this display is?
I wonder where the information on this display is coming from.

Texts.Eng: This looks like it might be important, but really I have no idea.
